rows.label: bf11530100_0010
rows.name: Should we really be bringing the kids along?

rows.label: bf11530100_0020
rows.name: Are you worried?

rows.label: bf11530100_0030
rows.name: Mhm...

rows.label: bf11530100_0040
rows.name:
Alst is a dangerous place right now.
The war reaches everywhere.

rows.label: bf11530100_0050
rows.name: I'm sure we can keep them safe in a normal fight, but if...

rows.label: bf11530100_0060
rows.name: [ML:undisp ][ML:Dash ]

rows.label: bf11530100_0070
rows.name: Where are you going?

rows.label: bf11530100_0080
rows.name: I want to speak with Adel.

rows.label: bf11530100_0090
rows.name: At this time of night?

rows.label: bf11530100_0100
rows.name:
I'll see what he thinks about it.
And if his mind is made up, there's still no harm done.

rows.label: bf11530100_0110
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Aaaaahhhh!

rows.label: bf11530100_0120
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Waa!

rows.label: bf11530100_0130
rows.name: How long have you been there?!

rows.label: bf11530100_0140
rows.name: Hey! What are you doing in my bed?

rows.label: bf11530100_0150
rows.name: Huh? What are you talking about?

rows.label: bf11530100_0160
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Gyah!!

rows.label: bf11530100_0170
rows.name: Get out! Interloper! Monster!

rows.label: bf11530100_0180
rows.name: Hey, quit it!

rows.label: bf11530100_0190
rows.name: Wh-?! This is where I sleep!

rows.label: bf11530100_0200
rows.name: It ain't your bed, lady!

rows.label: bf11530100_0210
rows.name: Ow...

rows.label: bf11530100_0220
rows.name:
Ohhh you're such a pain in everyone's bum,
you know that? You simpleton!

rows.label: bf11530100_0230
rows.name: Hey, wait a minute!

rows.label: bf11530100_0240
rows.name: Calm down, both of you... Ow!

rows.label: bf11530100_0250
rows.name: Come on, take it down a no-no-no-NO...!

rows.label: bf11530100_0260
rows.name: What's all the noise? Is something up?

rows.label: bf11530100_0270
rows.name: Uhm... It's probably better to sit this one out...

rows.label: bf11530100_0280
rows.name: Perhaps that's wise.

rows.label: bf11530100_0290
rows.name: Yeah. Maybe I'll just...ask him tomorrow...
